  18 Sep 2007; Andreas Proschofsky <suka@gentoo.org>
  +files/2.3.0/disable-regcomp-java.diff,
  +files/2.3.0/disable-regcomp-python.diff, +files/2.3.0/ooo-env_log.diff,
