  case notes for more details).

*openoffice-1.1_rc3 (20 Aug 2003)

  20 Aug 2003; Paul de Vrieze <pauldv@gentoo.org> openoffice-1.1_rc3.ebuild,
  files/1.1_rc3/fixed-gcc.patch, files/1.1_rc3/newstlportfix.patch,
